      <title>匈牙利通胀放缓，央行谨慎降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/hungary-cpi-drops-to-target-as-central-bank-cautious-on-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利通胀率已放缓至央行的目标水平，但货币疲软、地缘政治风险加剧以及今年剩余时间价格上涨预期加速，可能会阻止政策制定者继续实施货币宽松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/hungary-cpi-drops-to-target-as-central-bank-cautious-on-rate-cut</guid>
